Vne3l9DPCeM.title: 2010 6/19 【W 杯】サッカー日本対オランダ 静止画ハイライト 日本の完敗
Vne3l9DPCeM.description: 日本0-1オランダ この試合惜敗と報道されてますが、日本の完敗ではないでしょうか。オランダは、最小限の力で90分間戦い、後半開始8分間だけ全力で点を奪いに来て、1点入った後は、ある程度日本に攻撃させつつ、試合をコントロールしていました。日本は、メキシコのように相手をうまくコントロールして、ゲームを作る事がまだ出来ません。最終ラインの選手達が、海外でプレイしていないので、最終ラインのボール回しでゲームをコントロール出来ない、サイドバックのクロスの精度が悪すぎて、攻撃の起点になれない この2点だけでも早く改善してもらいたいです。次のデンマーク戦はツートップが、見たいです。後は、実況するアナウンサーがくだらない事をしゃべらなければいいんだけど、鈴木健アナじゃあ無理だろうなあ

About West Bromwich Albion:

West Bromwich Albion Football Club, also known as West Brom, the Baggies, the Throstles, or simply Albion, currently play in the English Barclays Premier League. 
Established in 1878, Albion has a proud heritage and rich tradition as one of the 12 founder members of England's Football League. 

The club won the Football League Championship in 1920 and are five-time FA Cup winners (1888, 1892, 1931, 1954 & 1968).
 
Strong footballing principles remain at the core of the club and its progressive thinking has seen it thrive on and off the pitch on a global stage, while not forgetting its roots. 
 
The home of the 'Baggies' -The Hawthorns -- has a 26,586 capacity and sits in a central location in the Midlands. 
 
Like the club's state-of-the-art training facilities, the stadium offers the ideal backdrop for Barclays Premier League football. 
 
It remains a hive of activity all-year round as the club's directors and staff ensure everything is in place to remain competitive year after year in the biggest league in the world.

E6QcgEusg7s.description:
http://booredatwork.com/2013/02/25/steelseries-flux-in-ear-pros-gaming-headphones-pure-awesomeness/

http://steelseries.com/products/audio/steelseries-flux-in-ear-pro-headset

Twitter: http://twitter.com/booredatwork

Twitter- http://twitter.com/Say2words

Twitter- http://twitter.com/booredfemme

Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/pages/Booredatwork/211909969459

Google+: https://plus.google.com/b/107460054073872296956

Empireavenue: http://www.empireavenue.com/boored

Pinterest-  http://pinterest.com/booredatwork/

A few weeks ago we reviewed the well crafted SteelSeries Flux in-ear headphones. Today we take a look at the Fluax in-ear Pro gaming headphones. Featuring balanced armature driver technology, the Flux In-ear Pro headset is the most accurate headset SteelSeries has ever produced. Experience a new dimension in your favorite games, music and movies, thanks to the highly detailed soundscape of the finely-tuned balanced armature drivers. The balanced armature driver requires no external air to produce sound. This means the driver can be made to be very small and it also means that it can be tuned very precisely. What you get is an enriching sound and feel that brings your gaming to another level.

Our swappable cable system offers full compatibility with mobile devices, PC and Mac, A mobile end with a single 3-pole 3.5mm jack and a PC cable with a 3.5mm headphone jack and a 3.5mm microphone jack have both been included. this headset can optionally be worn down. To achieve this you must switch the earbuds' intended sides; place the left earbud in your right ear and the right earbud in your left ear. The headphones come with  included memory foam tips for an even better audio experience. Also Include is a sleek yet compact carrying case to protect your headset. In addition, can hold your extra cable and ear tips. 

The Beauty with the SteelSeries Flux In-Ear Pro, besides the great build quality or the real tangle free cables, is truly the sound. You get rich balance audio, be it during your favorite session of Guild Wars 2 or taking a jog listening to your power running track. The balanced armature drivers really give you a clear and smooth audio feel with great bass, and clear audio with vocals sounding balanced at clear. Priced at $129.99 these are truly the first set of in-ear headphones that serve both the gamer and music lover in all of us.
